 | url    = https://books.google.com/books?id=BwistUlpZ7cC&pg=PA424
 | isbn   = 978-0534424718
 }}</ref> It is named after the [[Austria]]n physicist [[Christian Doppler]], who described the phenomenon in 1842.}}
